msgid "3. NVMEM cell based consumer APIs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/nvmem.rst:96
msgid ""
"NVMEM cells are the data entries/fields in the NVMEM. The NVMEM framework "
"provides 3 APIs to read/write NVMEM cells::"
